store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191540/extras/c9831827a6e48e1ce5f8996eb3752d85.poster.avif?t=1742811075\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191540/extras/c9831827a6e48e1ce5f8996eb3752d85.webm?t=1742811075\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191540/extras/c9831827a6e48e1ce5f8996eb3752d85.mp4?t=1742811075\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll have your own hands and all the power that comes with being the <strong>God of Death and Darkness</strong>, of course... Plus a wide selection of combos and abilities that will allow you to fight your way through the deepest corners of the Ragast.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Become part of the Ragast and join our community</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2191540/extras/5630c45cd4c48f3e9d4e6b412a577191.avif?t=1742811075\" width=616 height=110 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And once you enter the Ragast, you don't get out, but you fight with Morkull. So join Morkull's ranks and support his Machiavellian cause with the rest of his bannermen in our Morkull Ragast's Rage community.</p>",
